{
  "stem": "5810.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that, later on, will show where it did save my mother, and my sister, and my life later on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this is what happened in Malines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after interrogation we were put into detention cells with a lot of other Jews at the time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's exactly right, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then one by one, the rest of our family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was last being searched.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, there was nothing we were hiding at the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the money was quite safe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then something that I-- I still have a problem finding out about happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know whether my mother was able to make some kind of an arrangement or, as I understand it today, the Belgian queen at the time had appealed to the Germans in 1942-- it was still possible to do that-- for the-- for the saving of the children, to-- to not to be taken to concentration camps and so on.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or there was some kind of arrangement with somebody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But all I know is that my brother, my younger-- not my younger brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm the youngest.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the youngest of the brother before me, a sister who was a little bit older than I was, and myself were to be released.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my two-- my one brother and two sisters were to be taken at that time, they said, to work camps.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and my mother was to be taken.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember her pleading, saying that-- that she had no one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No one was there to take care of the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where would they go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What would they do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And whatever the situation was-- and I guess I'll never know, because nobody's alive today to be able to explain to me-- she was released with us.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
